{"title":"The new Specialized Sagan Collection includes a bandana because of course it does","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/specialized-sagan-collection-disruption/","date":1624636859000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_Detail-fd05a59.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=620,413\" />                                            <p><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/brand/specialized/\">Specialized</a> has announced its latest Sagan collection and, as ever, it includes some seriously fancy special edition versions of the brand’s S-Works flagship range, including the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/reviews/bikes/road-bikes/specialized-s-works-tarmac-sl7-review/\">S-Works Tarmac SL7</a> race bike, and the ultra-lightweight <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/reviews/bikes/road-bikes/specialized-s-works-aethos-dura-ace-di2-review/\">S-Works Aethos</a>.</p>\n<p>Called Disruption, the range celebrates Specialized’s most lauded rider, Peter Sagan, who currently rides for Bora–Hansgrohe and will be lining up alongside his teammates for the opening stage of the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/events/tour-de-france/\">2021 Tour de France</a> tomorrow.</p>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_4-ff57a28.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Peter Sagan, seen here on his way to the bank.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_5-54cb8c4.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>If this isn’t a reference to the green jersey, we’re terrible journalists. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_3-0a3eb86.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Something something column inches.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_2-54b1d0e.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>I can’t figure out what he’s holding here, but it’s probably expensive. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_1-d4ec24e.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>He looks dapper in blue too. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Accompanying the launch press release are some lovely photos of Peter Sagan doing normal one-percenter stuff like driving around a sun-soaked European city in a classic convertible, looking for all the world like he’s on his way to a regatta.</p>\n<p>We can’t see his feet, but I assume he’s wearing Italian loafers without socks.</p>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_Tarmac-SL7_Hero-b7b3c42.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The S-Works Tarmac is relatively restrained. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_Tarmac-SL7_Detail_Seat_Junction-d1c60c1.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Sagan is the Slovak national champion. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_Tarmac-SL7_Detail_Top_Tube-81a9bc6.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>There’s subtle gold detailing. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_Tarmac-SL7_Detail_Fork_Crown-da442a5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>This is understated, by previous Sagan standards. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>The new Sagan Collection S-Works Tarmac frameset is mostly a relatively restrained black that looks like it could just be clear-coat over carbon.</p>\n<p>There are small gold details, plus a rather cool flag of Slovakia on the back of the seat tube – Sagan is the Slovak national champion, don’t forget.</p>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_Aethos-12R_Hero-dc5de30.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The S-Works Aethos is all gold, all the time. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_Aethos-10R_Hero-5c2c16d.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The second-tier model is pretty nice too. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>The Aethos, meanwhile, comes in a gold S-Works version, or a luxurious off-white <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/2021-specialized-aethos-pro-expert/\">second-tier FACT 10r variant</a>, again with various gold detailing.</p>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_SW7-Pair_Hero-a27127d.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>These are nice, eh?</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_SW7_Detail_Back-a44c4f6.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Sagan will never again lose his shoes on the coach trip to Blackpool.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/Specialized_Sagan-Collection_Evade-Helmet_Hero-8f6a9a2.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The Evade helmet looks pretty classy. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Gold is everywhere in fact – the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/reviews/shoes/road-bike-shoes/specialized-s-works-7-shoes-review/\">S-Works 7 shoes</a>’ Boa dials and logos are gold, as is the S-Works badge on the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/reviews/helmets/road-cycling-helmets/specialized-s-works-evade-with-angi-review/\">Evade</a> aero helmet.</p>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/64821-511_APP_SAGAN-DISRUPTION-BANDANA-MULTI-OSFA_HERO-9a67087.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Is this disruptive enough for you?</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/64821-521_APP_SAGAN-DISRUPTION-DEFLECT-UV-CYCLING-CAP-MULTI-M_DETAIL1-08c68dd.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The cap is positively retro. </span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/06/64721-281_APP_SAGAN-DISRUPTION-SOFT-AIR-TALL-SOCK-WHT-M_HERO-39d97d8.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>You can’t really go wrong with Sagan socks.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Specialized</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>The range also includes socks, a cap and a bandana that’s said to be “the perfect addition that ties everything together”.</p>\n<p>The phrase “Sagan Collection Disruption Bandana” somehow feels extremely of this moment, don’t you think?</p>\n<h2>Specialized Sagan Collection–Disruption pricing</h2>\n<p>As with previous Sagan collections, products in the range are priced slightly above their standard range counterparts. Here’s the pricing we have so far:</p>\n<ul><li><strong>S-Works Tarmac Frameset:</strong> £4,750</li>\n<li><strong>Fact 10r Aethos frameset:</strong> £2,750</li>\n<li><strong>S-Works Evade II helmet:</strong> £250</li>\n<li><strong>S-Works 7 shoe:</strong> £370</li>\n</ul><p>For context, a regular S-Works Tarmac SL7 frameset currently retails at £4,250 / $5,500, while the S-Works Aethos frameset is £4,500 / $5,500.</p>","author":"Matthew Loveridge","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"aefabd4719f592ec692bfa8ae908038ae6ed29524afb949ac99a81b17f01502d","category":"Cycling"}